Subject: [PATCH v4 16/18] scripts: kernel-doc: improve nested logic to handle multiple identifiers
Date: Mon, 18 Dec 2017 10:30:17 -0200
Message-Id: <b89b7c5400afd8c03d88ccccd2b5edd3625a1997.1513599193.git.mchehab@s-opensource.com>
